{"tid":1275330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住呀手足，發夢見到你借件衫比我，我要扔左佢啦。","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:35:49.000Z","uid":149181,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76bb65531f18983d9577626b9e1f211174589657","tid":1275330,"uid":149181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"發夢見到自己好似貓咁獨來獨往，然後街上幾位手足幫左我，仲借左件衫比我保護我身上既<span style=\"color: red;\">疤痕</span>。<br />\n<br />\n但唔好意思啦，我唔小心<span style=\"color: red;\">咁整污糟哂身上既所有衫</span> ，而為左安全，我要扔左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想係度好好多謝幾位唔識既手足，多謝你地齊上齊落帶走左我。<br />\n<br />\n最後，所有手足要加油呀，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個都不能少</span>"},{"pid":"a86793d25071747db7e7667acc698a383c7cc273","tid":1275330,"uid":69525,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:45.000Z","msg":"你發夢咋 依家零晨3點都夢遊既<br />\n訓喇 乖豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你個夢"},{"pid":"e88e6fa68bcbf80a96e9376a863459c207340e41","tid":1275330,"uid":149181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a86793d25071747db7e7667acc698a383c7cc273","tid":1275330,"uid":69525,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:11:45.000Z","msg":"你發夢咋 依家零晨3點都夢遊既<br />\n訓喇 乖豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你個夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"希望個幾位手足發夢上連登睇到啦"},{"pid":"f0e38fa424927ee3d884dc1001425ffcedbe9718","tid":1275330,"uid":272353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"瞓啦巴絲，朝早起身再諗 或者瞓一陣先起身睇4點球賽"},{"pid":"24771de5dc2fa9bdccd2a3695c1aca7e6b95823a","tid":1275330,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"飲杯水繼續瞓 未有耐天光返工"},{"pid":"6ef4dd0480cdc54d4c0574e7df393d62cd8e07cf","tid":1275330,"uid":11948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20